OL,3,CCar crash victim died alone in
OL,4,Chospital after trust failed to call
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FA hospital trust has apologised for
OL,8,Ffailing to call the family of a man
OL,9,Fwho died in hospital a week after
OL,10,Fbeing involved in a car crash in Hull.
OL,12,FPeter Hayes, 76, was admitted to
OL,13,Fhospital after being involved in the
OL,14,Ftwo-vehicle crash in Great Hatfield on
OL,15,F29 May.
OL,17,FAs his injuries were not initially
OL,18,Fdeemed to be life-threatening, police
OL,19,Fdid not deploy anyone to inform the
OL,20,Ffamily.
