OL,7,FMr Hayes was transferred to Castle
OL,8,FHill Hospital in Cottingham, but died
OL,9,Fin hospital on 5 June. A post-mortem
OL,10,Fconcluded he died of natural causes.
OL,12,FNeither police nor hospital staff
OL,13,Fcontacted Mr Hayes' family until after
OL,14,Fhe had died.
OL,16,FMr Hayes' daughter Emma Hayes lives in
OL,17,FPreston. She said she would have
OL,18,Fdriven straight to Hull had she known
OL,19,Fwhat had happened.
