OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV, she said: "That
OL,8,Fabsolutely breaks my heart thinking
OL,9,Fabout him being on his own in hospital
OL,10,Ffor an entire week.
OL,12,F"What was going through his mind? Did
OL,13,Fhe ask for us?"
OL,15,FShe added: "I've got so many questions
OL,16,Fgoing round my head. I can't process
OL,17,Fthat he was in hospital for a week on
OL,18,Fhis own."
