OL,7,FThe lack of any phone call is now
OL,8,Fbeing investigated by the NHS, which
OL,9,Fhas also apologised for the error.
OL,11,FMs Hayes said "sorry" was not enough,
OL,12,Fadding it "would not give me that week
OL,13,Fback with my dad".
OL,15,FA spokeswoman for NHS Humber Health
OL,16,FPartnership said: "We would like to
OL,17,Fapologise to Mr Hayes's daughter Emma
OL,18,Ffor the distress we have caused.
OL,20,F"We launched an investigation after Ms
OL,21,FHayes contacted us with her concerns.
