OL,7,F"We have been in touch with her
OL,8,Fdirectly to report our findings and
OL,9,Foutline the steps our senior nursing
OL,10,Fteam are taking to ensure this mistake
OL,11,Fis never repeated.
OL,13,F"We accept we did not deliver the
OL,14,Fstandard of care our patients and
OL,15,Ftheir families expect on this occasion
OL,16,Fand we would like to assure Ms Hayes
OL,17,Fwe will learn from our error."
