OL,7,FA spokesperson for Humberside Police
OL,8,Fsaid: "To lose a loved one in any
OL,9,Fcircumstance is always a devastating
OL,10,Ftime to navigate through, and our
OL,11,Fthoughts and sympathies remain with Mr
OL,12,FHayes' family as they continue to
OL,13,Fgrieve for the loss of him. On
OL,14,FThursday, May 29, 2025, officers were
OL,15,Fcalled to attend Great Hatfield in
OL,16,FHull after we received reports of a
OL,17,Ftwo-vehicle road traffic collision.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
