OL,7,F"First responding officers who
OL,8,Fattended the scene continued to
OL,9,Fprogress lines of enquiries to
OL,10,Funderstand the circumstances
OL,11,Fsurrounding the collision however
OL,12,Fseven days after the collision, on
OL,13,FThursday, 5 June 2025, Mr Hayes sadly
OL,14,Fpassed away.
