OL,7,F"After every death following a road
OL,8,Ftraffic collision, an investigation is
OL,9,Fcarried out by our Serious Collisions
OL,10,FUnit to determine how the collision
OL,11,Foccurred. As part of this
OL,12,Finvestigation, a post mortem took
OL,13,Fplace where the Coroner concluded that
OL,14,FMr Hayes died from natural causes and
OL,15,Fno further enquiries needed to be
OL,16,Fcarried out by Humberside Police.
OL,18,F"A death in any circumstance is
OL,19,Fheartbreaking, and our thoughts will
OL,20,Falways remain with Mr Hayes' family."
